1. *Sobe* su uglavnom bile puno toplije nego ovde. (The rooms were usually much warmer than here.) 
2. On je uvek u svojoj *sobi*. (He is always in his room.)
3. *Sobama* smo stavili nove name≈°taje. (We put new furniture in the rooms.)
4. *Sobu* je uredila u stilu seoskog dvora. (She decorated the room in the style of a country manor.)
5. U *sobi* je bila jedna velika postelja. (There was one big bed in the room.)
6. Oni su se izgubili u nizu *soba*. (They got lost in a series of rooms.)